quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  26,20,"(Musa) naboola mbu: “Ndakhola ako olwa ndali nendi mubandu balia abakora."
  26,21,"Mana nebelukha olwa ndali nebarire, ne Nyasaye wanje Omulesi niyambelesia obwami, ne niyakhola okhuba Mubarumwa."
  26,22,"Ne echo nicho emikabo chiawumborolelangakhwo echia wakholela, ne wara Abana ba Israili mubusandi.”"
  26,23,"Firauni naboola mbu: “Ne Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi oyo ni wina?”"
  26,24,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye Omulesi owaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio, toto nimuli abokhusuubila nobwatoto.”"
  26,25,"(Firauni) Naboolela balia abali nibamubotokhane mumbeka wuwe mbu: “Koo, shimuwulilanga tawe?”"
  26,26,"(Musa) naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi nende Nyasaye Omulesi wa bapapa benyu abaranjilila.”"
  26,27,"(Firauni) naboola mbu: “Toto bwene Omurumwa wenyu owamwarumilwa ni omulalu.”"
  26,28,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Niye Nyasaye Omulesi wa Ebukwe nende Mumbo nende ebili hakari wabio, toto enywe nimuli mbu mwikhonyelanga obwongo.”"
  26,29,"(Firauni) naboola mbu: “Niwitsa okhusuubila nyasaye wundi ulali esie tawe, toto nditsa okhukhukhola obe mubaboye.”"
  26,30,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, kata nekhurerera eshindu shili mubwang’angu?”"
  26,31,"Naboola mbu: “Nakhashirerakhwo, toto noli mubandu baboolanga obwatoto.”"
  26,32,"Mana nasukuna hasi indabushi yiyie, lola, niikalukhana inzukha ilolekha."
  26,33,"Ne narusia omukhono kukwe, lola, nikuba omulafu tswe khubahenganga."
  26,34,"(Firauni) naboolela abakhongo bali nibamubotokhane mbu: “Toto uno ni omulosi umanyile muno."
  26,35,"Yenyanga okhubarusia mushialo shienyu nende obulosi bubwe, kho muboola murie?”"
  26,36,"Nibaboola mbu: “Mhelesie ebise ye nende omusiani wabu, ne orume mumatokho abandu bakhung’asinjia Abandu."
  26,37,"Balakhurerera buli omulosi omukhongo umanyile muno.”"
  26,38,"Kho, abalosi abo nibakhung’asibwa khulwa ebise nende inyanga imanyikhane."
  26,39,"Ne Abandu nibaboolelwa mbu: “Mumalile okhukhung’ana?"